== Exploring Node.js

Sample JSON API Application in Node.js

Technologies Used :
1 ) Node.js
2 ) Express Web Framework for Node.js
3 ) MongoDB

Routes : /users/:id GET
         /users/ POST
         /users/:id PUT
         /users/:id DELETE
         /users/ GET

Reference : AN Awesome Article Here

http://coenraets.org/blog/2012/10/creating-a-rest-api-using-node-js-express-and-mongodb/
